sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Application
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as Kueue Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Controller as Kueue Controller<br/>Manager
    participant Workload as Workload CRD
    participant ClusterQueue as ClusterQueue CRD
    participant Pods as Job Pods

    Note over User,Pods: Flow 1: Job Submission and Admission

    User->>K8sAPI: POST /apis/batch/v1/jobs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token/Client Cert
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Mutating webhook call<br/>mTLS
    Webhook->>Webhook: Create Workload CRD from Job spec
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Return mutated Job (suspended)
    K8sAPI-->>User: Job created (suspended)

    Webhook->>K8sAPI: Create Workload CRD<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Webhook: Workload created

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch Workload CRDs<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: New Workload event

    Controller->>Controller: Evaluate quota in ClusterQueue

    alt Resources Available
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Update Workload.status=Admitted<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Update Job (unsuspend)<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        K8sAPI->>Pods: Create Job Pods
        Pods-->>User: Job starts executing
    else No Resources
        Controller->>Workload: Update status=Pending<br/>Queue position
        Note over Controller,Workload: Job remains in queue<br/>until resources available
    end

    Note over User,Pods: Flow 2: Metrics Collection

    participant Prom as Prometheus
    participant MetricsSvc as kueue-metrics-service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Prom->>MetricsSvc: GET /metrics<br/>No auth
    MetricsSvc-->>Prom: Queue metrics<br/>(pending workloads, quotas, usage)

    Note over User,Pods: Flow 3: Visibility API Query

    participant CLI as User/CLI
    participant VisSvc as Visibility Server<br/>8082/TCP HTTPS TLS

    CLI->>K8sAPI: GET /apis/visibility.kueue.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1/<br/>clusterqueues/{name}/pendingworkloads<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>VisSvc: Proxy request<br/>ServiceAccount delegation
    VisSvc-->>K8sAPI: Pending workload list<br/>(positions, priorities)
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: JSON response

    Note over User,Pods: Flow 4: Cluster Autoscaler Integration

    participant AutoscaleAPI as autoscaling.x-k8s.io API
    participant Autoscaler as Cluster Autoscaler

    Controller->>Controller: AdmissionCheck requires provisioning
    Controller->>AutoscaleAPI: Create ProvisioningRequest<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    AutoscaleAPI->>Autoscaler: Trigger node provisioning
    Autoscaler-->>Controller: New nodes available
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Admit workload (resources now available)
